858
00:42:06.398 --> 00:42:08.190
You arrogant spoilt brat.

859
00:42:08.273 --> 00:42:08.982
Boss.

860
00:42:09.065 --> 00:42:10.814
teach him a lesson.

861
00:42:29.231 --> 00:42:30.523
Show me what got.

862
00:42:32.314 --> 00:42:33.440
You go.

863
00:42:33.523 --> 00:42:35.356
No. but. boss...

864
00:42:35.439 --> 00:42:37.398
how dare I steal your thunder?

865
00:42:37.481 --> 00:42:39.690
Fighting a child is
just embarrassing.

866
00:42:39.773 --> 00:42:41.773
When I say go. you go.

867
00:42:41.856 --> 00:42:43.106
Hey. k-k-kid.

868
00:42:43.189 --> 00:42:44.815
Since you're young and naive.

869
00:42:44.898 --> 00:42:46.273
I'm willing to let this slide.

870
00:42:46.356 --> 00:42:47.648
You. you...

871
00:42:47.731 --> 00:42:49.981
It's still not too late
to run home to mommy.

872
00:42:50.606 --> 00:42:51.149
