dodge to the right.

883
00:43:10.314 --> 00:43:11.731
Sorry. I thought it was left.

884
00:43:14.481 --> 00:43:15.815
So weak.

885
00:43:15.898 --> 00:43:16.524
Master Taiyi.

886
00:43:16.607 --> 00:43:17.856
