to steal our soup?

900
00:43:41.898 --> 00:43:43.314
This calls for a beating.

901
00:43:49.148 --> 00:43:49.816
So gross.

902
00:43:49.899 --> 00:43:53.606
Super Mighty Club Strike!

903
00:43:57.773 --> 00:43:58.399
See!

904
00:43:58.482 --> 00:43:59.773
I told you he was pretending.

905
00:44:00.439 --> 00:44:02.231
I wasn't paying attention.

906
00:44:02.314 --> 00:44:03.314
Not possible!

907
00:44:20.273 --> 00:44:22.981
Not possible!

908
00:44:29.856 --> 00:44:30.649
You suck!

909
00:44:30.732 --> 00:44:31.731
Step aside!

910
00:44:31.814 --> 00:44:32.898
Watch me kick his butt.

911
00:44:33.481 --> 00:44:34.565
Why did you spit it all out?

912
00:44:34.648 --> 00:44:35.690
The taste is too strong.

913
00:44:35.773 --> 00:44:36.607
I couldn't help it.

914
00:44:36.690 --> 00:44:38.148
Check this out!

915
00:44:41.398 --> 00:44:42.606
Funny!

916
00:44:42.814 --> 00:44:43.566
