917
00:44:43.649 --> 00:44:45.106
We can't win without the pill.

918
00:44:53.814 --> 00:44:54.856
Deero is watching.

919
00:44:54.939 --> 00:44:56.273
I can't give you the pill.

920
00:44:56.356 --> 00:44:57.565
What do we do now?

921
00:44:57.648 --> 00:44:59.065
I got it.

922
00:44:59.148 --> 00:45:01.565
There is another way.

923
00:45:01.648 --> 00:45:02.731
You're not suggesting...

924
00:45:02.814 --> 00:45:04.898
We can eat the puke.

925
00:45:04.981 --> 00:45:05.566
But.

926
00:45:05.649 --> 00:45:07.148
